1
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:07,540
=Live and Love S2=
=Live and Love: Spring Festival Special=

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:09,860
(Arena; Square; Dormitory;
Balance Zone; Dining Hall; Water Arena)

3
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:13,160
Attention, islanders.

4
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:15,920
Game time has begun.

5
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:17,120
(Fun Game Time)
Islanders,

6
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:19,400
please head to the dining hall
for the game.

7
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:20,800
President Huang.

8
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,160
Yan, your turn.

9
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,520
Guan, hurry up.

10
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,600
I think it's Wan.

11
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,440
Get ready to play.

12
00:00:30,590 --> 00:00:32,520
("Who Is the Glutton" Rules)
Before each round,

13
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:34,600
each player draw a role card.

14
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:37,720
(Before the game, draw a role card)
Role cards are Glutton or Civilian.

15
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:38,820
(Glutton or Civilian)

16
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,520
Night falls. Close your eyes.

17
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,000
Glutton,

18
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,280
during the allotted time at night,

19
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:46,840
without letting anyone notice,

20
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:48,800
secretly finish off the food

21
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,960
in front of any one player.

22
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:52,120
When time's up,
the sky turns bright.

23
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:54,400
After sunrise, everyone speaks in turn.

24
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,720
You noticed his lips were red, right?

25
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:57,640
(Eye‑catching red)

26
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,680
When I called your name,

27
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,520
you responded slowly.

28
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,000
After everyone speaks,

29
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,000
vote for

30
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,400
who you think is the Glutton.

31
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,360
If Civilians outnumber the Glutton,

32
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,600
Civilians win.

33
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,200
Civilians with the right vote,

34
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,960
give the Glutton a Truth or Dare.

35
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,120
Brother.

36
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:15,080
(Glutton)
But if the Glutton gets away,

37
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,760
they get to punish the Civilians.

38
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,800
Penalty?

39
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,160
Eat a slice of lemon.

40
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:21,080
Draw a card.

41
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,780
(Who Is the Glutton, Round One)

42
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,080
Alright, confirm your roles.

43
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,500
(Confirming roles)

44
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,040
Okay.

45
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,400
Eyes closed.

46
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,560
(Night falls. Close your eyes)

47
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,840
I'll pick the snacks.

48
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:34,120
What food will you choose?

49
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,240
(Can't wait)
Rice crackers?

50
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:35,880
(I love them.)

51
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:36,840
Let me hear it.

52
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,640
Who's gonna start munching later?

53
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:39,880
In...

54
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,000
sixty seconds.

55
00:01:44,060 --> 00:01:46,160
(Who Is the Glutton, Round One.
Food: Potato Chips)

56
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,760
Glutton, open your eyes.

57
00:01:47,820 --> 00:01:50,500
(Glutton)

58
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:51,700
(Action starts)

59
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:52,940
(Pick the food in front of her)

60
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:54,500
(Listening intently)

61
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,940
(Big bite)

62
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:58,340
(Dodging)

63
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,250
(Unaware)
Can we talk

64
00:01:59,250 --> 00:02:00,280
when our eyes are closed?

65
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:00,840
Sure.

66
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,640
You can chat away.

67
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,190
(Testing)
Has the Glutton eaten?

68
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,840
The Glutton hasn't eaten.

69
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,540
(Misdirecting)

70
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:06,280
Who is

71
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:06,880
staying quiet?

72
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:07,500
(Testing)
Who?

73
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,840
Speak up, everyone say something.

74
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,240
The quiet one is the Glutton.

75
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,120
Yiija.

76
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,740
(I'm not.)

77
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:12,840
(Empty plate)

78
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,920
(Mission complete)
Who?

79
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:15,990
(Handling carefully)
Eyes closed.

80
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,120
Night ends.

81
00:02:20,020 --> 00:02:21,980
(Observing)

82
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:23,260
(Looking around)

83
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,480
The chips are gone.

84
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,820
(Completely empty)

85
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,380
(A bit guilty)

86
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,880
(Accusation)
Everyone speaks one.

87
00:02:30,110 --> 00:02:30,800
(Eager)
Let's start.

88
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,680
You go first.

89
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,480
I think it's Wan.

90
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:35,440
(Zhu Huiyan, Ding Wanning)
When we talked,

91
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,280
I felt like

92
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,280
she had something

93
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,280
in her mouth.

94
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,720
I always talk like this.

95
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:40,960
Trust me.

96
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,700
(My habit)

97
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:43,580
(Suspicious?)

98
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,400
Guan, your turn.

99
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,640
I think it's Wan.

100
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,360
(Wu Guanjie suspects Ding Wanning)

101
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,160
Her crunching sound

102
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,680
was so loud just now.

103
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,480
Right?

104
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,260
(Locating the sound)

105
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,080
If it was her,

106
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,300
why would she eat her food?

107
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,360
(A new thought)
Exactly!

108
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,640
(Jumps in)
Would I be that dumb?

109
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,480
To fool us.

110
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,680
It'll make us

111
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,720
(Explaining)
look sharp.

112
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,440
But after the night ended,

113
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,640
Guan licked his lips.

114
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:05,260
(Caught in real-time)

115
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:07,840
(Spots a detail)
I saw that too.

116
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,520
Kind of suspicious.

117
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:11,860
(Agrees)

118
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,280
Alright, it's fine.

119
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,440
Punish me then.

120
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:16,900
(Going with the flow)

121
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,000
He admitted.

122
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,120
See that?

123
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,480
Alright, get ready.

124
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:22,380
(Round One Voting)

125
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,480
Three, two, one, vote.

126
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,360
Feels a bit off.

127
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,560
Okay.

128
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:29,120
(Results)
Guan is out.

129
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,680
(Wu Guanjie out)
The Glutton wins.

130
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,160
Was my voice really that loud?

131
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,840
I didn't hear a thing.

132
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,240
If you hadn't said anything,

133
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,320
I would've voted for Wan.

134
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,720
You confused us well.

135
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:45,640
(My bad)

136
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,200
I told you

137
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,760
I actually heard her there

138
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,680
making crunching sound.

139
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,400
Why did I even...

140
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:49,920
Why did you…

141
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,100
(Accusing)
You don't even believe me.

142
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,660
(Reflecting)

143
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:56,080
I thought you admitted it.

144
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,160
Time for a penalty.

145
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,720
(Round One Penalty)
Dare?

146
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:02,860
(Thinking)

147
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,640
How about you guys finish these chips?

148
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,640
(Civilians eat chips)

149
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,040
Thanks, that's a nice punishment.

150
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,380
(This punishment hits the spot)

151
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,680
My turn now, sit down.

152
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:16,520
(Lu Yanting and Huang Jiawei
take turns hosting)

153
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,400
This is so much fun.

154
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,280
(Enjoyment level: Max)

155
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:19,240
It's about food.

156
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,820
(As long as they're happy)

157
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:22,940
(Who Is the Glutton, Round Two)

158
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:25,700
(Shuffling cards)

159
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,080
She's pretending.

160
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:29,740
(Suspicious)

161
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:30,820
(Seeking clarity)

162
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:34,380
(Confirming roles)

163
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,240
Alright, close your eyes.

164
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:38,240
(Night falls. Close your eyes.)

165
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:41,680
Three, two, one, Glutton, open your eyes.

166
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:43,300
(Glutton again)

167
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:45,140
(Food: premium sour strawberries)

168
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,020
(Got the food)

169
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,160
Come on, let's talk.

170
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,620
(Took it back)
Speak.

171
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:51,600
(Switching target)
Yan?

172
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,320
(Eating)
Not me.

173
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:52,780
Guan.

174
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,960
Glutton has to finish the whole plate.

175
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,260
(Seriously?)

176
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,760
Finish the whole plate... who?

177
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:07,560
Guan.

178
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,960
(Caught live – unfinished plate)

179
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,540
(Snuck a strawberry in the chaos)
Guan.

180
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,260
(Strawberries left)

181
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,840
Wan, say something.

182
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,960
What the heck is that?

183
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,120
Hey, I'm talking here.

184
00:05:16,220 --> 00:05:17,540
(Help! Someone please "save" me!)

185
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,280
Village Chief, say something.

186
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,360
What's up?

187
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,960
I'm talking.

188
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,640
Say that again.

189
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,120
(Attack mode)
Wan, your turn.

190
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,480
I give up.

191
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,760
Hold on.

192
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,640
Alright, it's Wan.

193
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,180
(Excited)

194
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,280
I gave up.

195
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,440
He told me to eat the whole plate.

196
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,800
Do you know
how many strawberries there were?

197
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,360
(Many)
I already ate one.

198
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,960
Do you even know how many?

199
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,380
(Defeated by strawberries)
Truth or Dare.

200
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,440
(Round Two Penalty)
I have one.

201
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:43,560
Pick any guy here

202
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,720
and tell him your confession.

203
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,500
(Penalty: Glutton picks a guy and confesses.)

204
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:54,480
Alright.

205
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,040
Here we go.

206
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,740
(The chosen one)

207
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,740
("I Confessed to My Crush.")

208
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:57,440
You know what?

209
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,840
The first time I saw you,

210
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,920
(Trying not to laugh)
I fell deeply in love.

211
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,560
You're my one and only.

212
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:07,260
(Holding it in)
You're my one and only.

213
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,090
(Holding back)
In next life...

214
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,960
No, let's be together in this life.

215
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,480
Do you want to be with me?

216
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,240
Okay?

217
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,920
(Holding back)
Yes, I do.

218
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,120
Yes, I do.

219
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,440
No way.

220
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:27,260
(Finally ending this "comedy show")

221
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,320
I'll be the host.

222
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:32,660
(Lu Yanting and Chen Yijia
take turns hosting)

223
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:33,880
Can I be the Glutton?

224
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,480
Please?

225
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,200
(Getting eager)

226
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:35,600
Are you

227
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,200
asking me to rig the game?

228
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,940
(Fair and square)

229
00:06:40,060 --> 00:06:41,820
(Who Is Glutton, Round Three)

230
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,840
Come on, draw a card.

231
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:52,260
(Confirming roles)

232
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,780
(Something's off with you)

233
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:54,980
(Again?)

234
00:06:54,980 --> 00:07:00,620
(Confirming roles)

235
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,120
You, my friend, seem shady.

236
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,430
(Fight back)
You're all shady.

237
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,440
Am I?

238
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,400
(Misheard words)
It's fine.

239
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:08,960
Listen later.

240
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,600
Alright.

241
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,400
Eyes closed.

242
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,920
Everyone, close your eyes.

243
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:13,640
(Night falls. Close your eyes.)

244
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,400
Okay.

245
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:17,040
Now, Glutton, open your eyes.

246
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:21,000
(Strike first)
Speak.

247
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,850
Who?

248
00:07:21,850 --> 00:07:23,000
(Food: Pistachio)
Speak now.

249
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,690
(Take the chance)

250
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:24,480
Say something.

251
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,600
Yanting, it must be you.

252
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,520
Lu.

253
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,320
(Seconded)

254
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:27,760
Mr. Huang.

255
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,090
(Responding)
President Huang.

256
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:30,600
What is the deal

257
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,960
with that multi-billion project?

258
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:35,400
(Your President Huang is online)
I'm here.

259
00:07:35,850 --> 00:07:37,200
(Got the chance)
President Huang.

260
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,200
(Your turn)
Yan, speak.

261
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,000
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

262
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,000
Yan, say something.

263
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,600
Quick.

264
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,320
Village Chief.

265
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,100
(I'm heading over)

266
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,520
(The scene falls into chaos)
Yanting.

267
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,720
(Swaps empty plates)
Guan.

268
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,680
Jiawei.

269
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,120
(This round's hot topic)
I'm here.

270
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,800
(Focus on the task)
My ear…

271
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:53,360
(Chew quickly)

272
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,320
Alright, time's up.

273
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,760
Okay, everyone open your eyes.

274
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:01,140
(Avoiding eye contact)

275
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,000
Guan.

276
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,320
Guan.

277
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,120
Was it you?

278
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:06,800
Guan.

279
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:10,200
I was speaking loud.
How did you miss it?

280
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,400
Who is this? Kinda...

281
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,640
No, it's definitely her.

282
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:16,640
Me again?

283
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,440
